      "body" : "I would have no problem with this as long as the transactions you are replacing have lower fee rates, and if you never prioritize transactions above others which have a higher fee rate (making the decision to do so irrational). I really dont think we should be adding new behavior which is not in a rational miner's best interest, we should be moving the other way (ie eventual RBF, etc).",
